<subSubSection id="AC0D082B7635E3438C90742937D7EDA9" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" type="names">
<paragraph id="A814B50A3377DD47931C0D3351AF76A4" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">Names.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FD576D6492043DA62397B459401E9D4F" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">
<emphasis id="E1FC2C083367D616E3DB74F711AF6CA8" bold="true" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">Myanmar</emphasis>
: 
<emphasis id="91919405E05EFB85BAD8808747F9F138" italics="true" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">payoke-aye</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="D30F870102288440A44A737E54B1EA9C" italics="true" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">pusi-nan</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="29E28CA3FAD52E24548D796DD3BD1E0D" italics="true" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">budi-nan</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="9C3CAE505F264A27C7E79E66EAE862F5" bold="true" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">English</emphasis>
: corn mint, field mint, japanese mint, wild mint.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="4D20C9D922B31BE330DAAEBDEA24E7C4" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" type="range">
<paragraph id="C4CF64CC5D67D4EED9504193016DFA73" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">Range.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A693B9876F84751F72AFEDD9A3B4D581" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">Europe and Asia. Cultivated throughout Myanmar, but thrives most in temperate climates.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="BF130E45EFC62222012B34B7F87A8F5F" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" type="conservation status">
<paragraph id="CAAD65C0FD4CB9E106EC5F738FF94F7B" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">Conservation status.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0F724026455F7CB5D3CF6A5667F8596D" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">
Least Concern [LC] (
<bibRefCitation id="EAD4726E4B58AD62E6D8192831B45404" author="IUCN" journalOrPublisher="African Journal of Traditional, Complementary, and Alternative Medicines" pageId="173" pageNumber="174" publicationUrl="http://www.iucnredlist.org/" refId="B117" refString="IUCN, 2017. IUCN Red List of threatened species. IUCN, Gland. http://www.iucnredlist.org/" title="IUCN Red List of threatened species. IUCN, Gland." url="http://www.iucnredlist.org/" year="2017">IUCN 2017</bibRefCitation>
